headline: Electronic Arts (EA) Surges in 2025 Ahead of $55 Billion Buyout Deal
summary: The Harbor Capital Advisors released its “Mid Cap Value Fund’s” Q4 2025 investor letter. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. Harbor Mid Cap Value Fund, subadvised by LSV Asset Management, delivered solid outperformance in the fourth quarter of 2025, with the Institutional Class returning 4.07% versus 1.42% for the Russell Midcap Value […]
